caption.body: Filmmaker Glen Milner profiles the Almonte horsemen as they drive more than one thousand horses across the Spanish plains in a five-centuries-old tradition that is central to their identity and reflects their harmony with the natural world.  See "The Horsemen" by Glen Milner, now playing, in the Video Arts screening room located pre-security, in the International Terminal.
